data.description:
Welcome home to this spacious 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath. Open floor plan. Situated on a cul-de-sac with a very large, fully fenced lot. Gated community. Bixby Schools. Small, quiet neighborhood. Ready to move in!

Tenants responsible for all utilities. HOA fees included in the rent. Pets allowed, no smoking inside the house.
